positive.review:
Really good xianxia cultivation RPG, probably the best xianxia game I played.

The game does drag on at the end but overall, it was a really good experience
Crazy good story line and customization of battle
贊

Really good xianxia cultivation RPG, probably the best xianxia game I played.

The game does drag on at the end but overall, it was a really good experience
修仙游戏，玩一玩还行。比较chill。有种玩网游但是又不可氪金的感觉。整体还行。

整体还可以，叠毒流不错。
问题就是，宁王府那个剧情杀让人直接幻灭。作为冠军的我，六天享乐两天就算了，还要这六天中的特定天数出门或者是逛逛才能触发其它剧情，否则就是做成药引子的剧情杀。整个人都麻了。不玩了。
Crazy good story line and customization of battle
